                    <figure>
                        <blockquote class="blockquote mt-5">
                            <p class="mb-0" style="text-align:justify;">The Fundação Gino Favaro 2nd objective is to contribute and support the development of the Educational Sector including operating Practical Training Facilities in Co-ordination and Co-operation with the relevant Authorities. The following are the list of the steps in attaining this objective.</p>
                            <ul>
                              <li>To assist and develop further the education sector, and engage in and develop Practical Training Facilities for various industries including hospitality and tourism sectors.</li>
                              <li>To further enhance the Skills Development and Work Experiences of local students in the relevant industries.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </blockquote>
                    </figure>
                    <p style="text-align:justify;">The Fundação has a very strong desire to operate Practical Training Facilities in several different industries in-order to compliment the Teachings and Services of the Technical & Vocational Schools currently operating in Timor-Leste, Government and non-Government. The importance of these practical training facilities is to offer “Real Time”, “Hands On” experience & opportunities to further enhance the Skills Development and On the Job Experience & Working Knowledge for local students.</p>
                    <p style="text-align:justify;">The desires of the Directors of the Fundação Gino Favaro are to assist Timor-Leste become a much sort after Tourism location in South East Asia. Naturally, this cannot be done without developing special facilities designed to enhance skills and working knowledge of each student in the relevant industries. <span class="fw-bold">“We have Labor Galore, it’s Professional Skills we need more.”</span></p>

